    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>One more option to do this:</p>\n<p>For <strong>Windows</strong> user:</p>\n<p><kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Alt</kbd> + <code>Left mouse click</code> on type, method etc.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/SD7XD.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/SD7XD.png\" alt=\"You will get this\" /></a></p>\n"
